      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#166534",
      "originalText": "遞歸循環：原始文本 → 名詞高亮 → 點擊名詞 → LLM 生成解釋 → 新文本窗 → 新名詞高亮 → ...",
      "autoResize": true
    },

    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t_cycle2",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 618,
      "text": "每次 LLM 回傳時，technicalTerms[] 自動註冊進 TermRegistry → 下層窗口自動識別新名詞 (無限遞歸)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#757575",
      "originalText": "每次 LLM 回傳時，technicalTerms[] 自動註冊進 TermRegistry → 下層窗口自動識別新名詞 (無限遞歸)",
      "autoResize": true
    },

    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "i1",
      "x": 55,
      "y": 720,
      "text": "type TextSegment = { kind: 'text', content: string } | { kind: 'term', content: string }",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "originalText": "type TextSegment = { kind: 'text', content: string } | { kind: 'term', content: string }",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "i2",
      "x": 55,
      "y": 738,
      "text": "interface ITermRegistry { isTerm(text): bool, getSortedTerms(): string[], register*(term, source?): void }",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "originalText": "interface ITermRegistry { isTerm(text): bool, getSortedTerms(): string[], register*(term, source?): void }",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "i3",
      "x": 55,
      "y": 756,
      "text": "interface ILLMService { explain(term): Promise<{ explanation: string, technicalTerms: string[] }> }",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "originalText": "interface ILLMService { explain(term): Promise<{ explanation: string, technicalTerms: string[] }> }",
      "autoResize": true
    },

